  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Holiday Club Apartments are on a self catering basis. Each apartment has its own equipped kitchen and dining table. The well stocked supermarket is around a ten minute walk (600 metres from the Holiday Club Hotel). Additionally there is a range of local restaurants in the resort (pay locally).</p>
<p>There is the option to upgrade to half board at the Holiday Club Hotel. Enjoy a breakfast buffet with a range of hot and cold options served between 7-10am, and a three course evening buffet with a choice of dishes available from 4-8pm.</p>
<p> </p>]]></cateringDescription>
  <deactivateThisPage>0</deactivateThisPage>
  <description><![CDATA[<p>Located in the centre of <span><a data-udi="umb://document/b8a6a8fa31c94e959dc5959c1881f2d5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b8a6a8fa31c94e959dc5959c1881f2d5}" title="Saariselka">Saariselkä</a>, the Holiday Club Apartments have</span> great access to the cross country ski trails and the ski slopes - which are just a short bus ride away.</p>
<h2>Perfect for families </h2>
<p>The Holiday Club Apartments offer cosy and traditional accommodation in a central location. Each apartment is spacious and <span>features modern kitchens and bathrooms, plus open plan living rooms with fireplaces - perfect for warming up after a day in the snow. These apartments are ideal if you and your family are wanting your own private, cosy base on your Lapland holiday or ski break. </span></p>
<h2>Self-catering and dining options</h2>
<p>The apartments are offered on a self catering basis and each has its own equipped kitchen so you can whip up tasty meals in the comfort of your own apartment. There is a well stocked local supermarket, and if you don't feel like cooking there is a variety of restaurants dotted around <a data-udi="umb://document/b8a6a8fa31c94e959dc5959c1881f2d5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b8a6a8fa31c94e959dc5959c1881f2d5}" title="Saariselka"><span>Saariselkä</span></a> many of which serve traditional Lappish dishes, pizza's and burgers. You'll have the option to upgrade to half board at the nearby <a data-udi="umb://document/c661c78119c84b88b761eef9614441f2" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c661c78119c84b88b761eef9614441f2}" title="Holiday Club Spa Hotel">Holiday Club Hotel</a> so that you can fully relax on your holiday, with no need to cook! Fuel up for the day at the buffet breakfast which features a continental offering as well as additional hot options. In the evenings you can enjoy a three course buffet style meal, there is a choice of mains, as well as a daily children's option and a salad bar. </p>
<p> </p>]]></description>
