  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Two Bedroom Apartments</strong> <span>are around 53m² </span>sleeping two to six people with two bedrooms and a double sofa bed in the living room. These apartments are offered on a self catering board basis, and have an equipped kitchen, living room and balcony. These apartments are located in an annexe a short walk away from the main Holiday Club building.</p>
